  "title": "Jade - Stardew Valley Wiki",
  "description": "Jade is a Mineral that can be found in Jade Nodes and Gem Nodes in the Mines (floors 40+), destroying barrels and crates (floors 40+), dropped by Blue Slimes and Dwarvish Sentries, in Fishing Treasure Chests, or received as a gift at the Feast of the Winter Star. Jade may also occasionally be found in a Garbage Can after the player has reached the bottom of the mines.",
